API Documentation

class DOMStringList

package js.html

A type returned by some APIs which contains a list of DOMString (strings).

Documentation DOMStringList by Mozilla Contributors, licensed under CC-BY-SA 2.5.

See:

https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMStringList

Variables

read onlylength:Int

Returns the length of the list,

Methods

contains (string:String):Bool

Returns Boolean indicating if the given string is in the list

item (index:Int):String

Returns a DOMString.
